glitz: an OpenGL image compositing library.
glitz:
glitz: Glitz is an OpenGL image compositing library. Glitz provides
glitz: Porter/Duff compositing of images and implicit mask generation for
glitz: geometric primitives including trapezoids, triangles, and rectangles.
glitz: Glitz can be used as a stand-alone layer above OpenGL but is also
glitz: designed to act as a backend for cairo, providing it with
glitz: OpenGL accelerated output.
